question: What is the name of the administrative center of Cēsu novads (Cēsis county) in Latvia?
asked_question_translated: Apa nama pusat pemerintahan Cēsu novads (kabupaten Cēsis) di Latvia?
answer: Nama pusat pemerintahan Cēsu novads di Latvia adalah Cēsis.
answer_translated_eng: The name of the centre of the Cēsu novads in Latvia is Cēsis.
